STYLESHEET.CSS
#box1{
      width: 800;
      height: 300px;
      float: left;
      
      background: blue;
      background: linear-gradient (blue, yellow)
}



Notes:
渐变色：
background: linear-gradient (blue, yellow)    从上到下是“蓝色”渐变成“黄色”
background: linear-gradient (to right, blue, yellow)    从“左”到“右”(right)是“蓝色”渐变成“黄色”
background: linear-gradient (to top right, blue, yellow)    从“左下”到“右上”(top right)是“蓝色”渐变成“黄色”
background: linear-gradient (blue, yellow 20%)    “蓝色”占上层的20%，余下80%为“黄色”
background: linear-gradient (30deg, blue, yellow)     30度倾斜渐变
background: linear-gradient (green, blue, yellow)    上中下渐变顺序为“绿蓝黄”
拼接色：
background: linear-gradient (blue 50%, yellow 50%)     无渐变区域
